<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Unsubstantial" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Unsubstantial,</orth> immaterial, incorporeal: <cit><quote>that u. death is amorous,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.103" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 3, 103</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thou u. air that I embrace,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 1, 7</bibl></cit>.
